House Resolution 638
By: Representatives Scott of the 76th, Schofield of the 63rd, and Davis of the 87th
A RESOLUTION
1 Recognizing and commending Mr. Hanan Abdul-Wahab on his outstanding public service;
2 and for other purposes.
3 WHEREAS, Mr. Hanan Abdul-Wahab, an Agricultural Engineer and Post-Harvest Expert,
4 serves as the Chief Executive Officer of the National Food Buffer Stock Company Ltd -
5 Ghana, where his impactful leadership has contributed to significant advancements in food
6 security and agricultural sustainability; and
7 WHEREAS, under Mr. Abdul-Wahab's visionary stewardship, NAFCO has undergone
8 remarkable reforms that have significantly bolstered Ghana's food security landscape,
9 including the revitalization of critical infrastructure and the establishment of transformative
10 partnerships that have fortified NAFCO's operational framework; and
11 WHEREAS, his leadership has facilitated the seamless distribution of food to Senior High
12 Schools across Ghana, a pivotal component of the nation's Free Senior High School program,
13 thereby enhancing nutritional standards and educational outcomes nationwide; and
